vernac_cmds: Definition e_P2 (b : wsort) (U : TS b) : nat := (fix F (w : wsort) (t : TS w) {struct t} : nat := match t with | var _ => 1 | app t0 t1 => S (F wt t0 + F wt t1) | lambda t0 => 2 * F wt t0 | env t0 t1 => F wt t0 * S (F ws t1) | id => 1 | shift => 1 | cons t0 t1 => S (F wt t0 + F ws t1) | comp t0 t1 => F ws t0 * S (F ws t1) | lift t0 => 4 * F ws t0 | meta_X _ => 1 | meta_x _ => 1 end) b U.
Theorem P2_pos : forall (b : wsort) (M : TS b), e_P2 _ M > 0.
simple induction M; simpl in |- *; intros; auto with arith.
Theorem P2_app : forall M N : terms, reg_app M N -> e_P2 _ M > e_P2 _ N.
simple induction 1; intros; simpl in |- *; elim Mult.mult_plus_distr_r; auto with arith.
Theorem P2_lambda : forall M N : terms, reg_lambda M N -> e_P2 _ M < e_P2 _ N.
change (2 * (e_P2 _ a * S (4 * e_P2 _ s)) > 2 * e_P2 _ a * S (e_P2 _ s)) in |- *.
